183
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:57,000
that there is a zero point energy

184
00:08:57,000 --> 00:08:58,000
for every quantum field.

185
00:08:58,000 --> 00:09:00,000
It's called vacuum energy.

186
00:09:00,000 --> 00:09:01,000
It's really there.

187
00:09:01,000 --> 00:09:03,000
Here's a measurement of it.

188
00:09:03,000 --> 00:09:05,000
In that sense, it's not mysterious.

189
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,000
It's a mathematical consequence

190
00:09:06,000 --> 00:09:08,000
of quantum field theory.

191
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:10,000
The really mysterious thing

192
00:09:10,000 --> 00:09:12,000
is not that there is vacuum energy

193
00:09:12,000 --> 00:09:14,000
or dark energy or whatever you want to call it.

194
00:09:14,000 --> 00:09:16,000
The really mysterious thing

195
00:09:16,000 --> 00:09:18,000
is that there's so little of it.

196
00:09:18,000 --> 00:09:20,000
That's the really mysterious thing.

197
00:09:20,000 --> 00:09:22,000
Why is there so little of it?

198
00:09:22,000 --> 00:09:23,000
I understand that.

199
00:09:23,000 --> 00:09:26,000
But then they say this mysterious thing

200
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:27,000
