249
00:11:29,000 --> 00:11:32,000
it turned out that it was there.

250
00:11:32,000 --> 00:11:33,000
All right?

251
00:11:33,000 --> 00:11:37,000
So it was an entirely a psychological

252
00:11:37,000 --> 00:11:39,000
mysteriousness.

253
00:11:39,000 --> 00:11:41,000
We convinced ourselves that there must be

254
00:11:41,000 --> 00:11:43,000
an explanation of its absence,

255
00:11:43,000 --> 00:11:45,000
and then when it wasn't absent,

256
00:11:45,000 --> 00:11:46,000
everybody said,

257
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:47,000
wow, oh my goodness,

