1116
00:49:33,480 --> 00:49:37,480
In fact, in which the thermal energy scales

1117
00:49:37,480 --> 00:49:41,480
were, let's say, way up here somewheres.

1118
00:49:41,480 --> 00:49:44,480
In that situation, it would be thermal equilibrium

1119
00:49:44,480 --> 00:49:47,480
