1127
00:50:08,480 --> 00:50:12,480
particles and antiparticles, bosons and fermions,

1128
00:50:12,480 --> 00:50:15,480
all more or less equally abundant

1129
00:50:15,480 --> 00:50:19,480
and pretty much determined by the thermal equilibrium

1130
00:50:19,480 --> 00:50:20,480
that takes place.

