00:50:20,480 --> 00:50:22,480
If there were too many ordinary particles

1132
00:50:22,480 --> 00:50:24,480
and not enough super particles,

1133
00:50:24,480 --> 00:50:28,480
then the collisions of ordinary particles

1134
00:50:28,480 --> 00:50:30,480
